{"tid":723721,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"或是對澳真不太理解丫埃 墨爾本悉尼雙城記","createTime":"2018-06-30T15:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T07:15:17.000Z","uid":192935,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"75a8b5a4971c1d3cd269c29de568abe61fa370bc","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"五月中決定裸辭之後，就即刻打上Asia Miles 出飛，將僅餘的45000里用左佢，好彩只係打左半個鍾就有人聽，補多$988稅成功出飛 <br />\n<br />\n雖然係45000里之下，舊制Asia Miles仲可以包埋去布里斯本同凱恩斯的內陸機，但因為去程同回程都冇位，可惜用唔盡張飛 <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 <br />\nCX135 HKG-&gt; MEL (19:05-06:15+1) <br />\n<br />\nDay 2 <br />\n墨爾本市區 <br />\n<br />\nDay 3 <br />\n菲利浦島 Local Tour <br />\n<br />\nDay 4 <br />\n大洋路 Local Tour <br />\n<br />\nDay 5 <br />\nQF422 MEL-&gt;SYD (10:00-11:25) 悉尼市區 <br />\n<br />\nDay 6 <br />\n藍山 <br />\n<br />\nDay 7 <br />\n塔龍加動物園 <br />\n<br />\nDay 8 <br />\nCX110 SYD-&gt; HKG (07:35-15:20) <br />\n<br />\n事前準備: 唱左700AUD，其實應該都唱多左幾多 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/210054_567d0191f6dec0940b81a075ba5ae6ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F210054_567d0191f6dec0940b81a075ba5ae6ec.jpg&h=cf3974cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10天 1.8GB 上網卡，係KXXXK買，機場拎，$100 (其實買貴左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/210334_40f9f6fcd5aa22aa2cfe8a63190c2b89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F210334_40f9f6fcd5aa22aa2cfe8a63190c2b89.jpg&h=5d15bede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毒向左走向右走冇乜野帶 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/210713_1047e67db79a9b758eee0afc9b308950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F210713_1047e67db79a9b758eee0afc9b308950.jpg&h=d2e7e310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公廁Lounge 好向左走向右走難食，野食全部凍向左走向右走哂 <br />\n其實最主要想拎枝水姐，不過唔知點解臨上機要check 多次hand carry (應該因為飛澳洲)，結果被人丟向左走向右走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/210840_a8ec2f9bee8ffa77a8363e417bfb0e0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F210840_a8ec2f9bee8ffa77a8363e417bfb0e0f.jpg&h=8e0b41b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/211414_062eca345c66c31536235cfb3fa34f72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F211414_062eca345c66c31536235cfb3fa34f72.jpg&h=bae5b27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等左呢個機會好耐，終於搭到A350 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/211602_bd48196fd38242e6c80b956e811f4465.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F211602_bd48196fd38242e6c80b956e811f4465.jpg&h=7377538d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/211816_73a6e0cc9d0b3ee65c4cd98d5cc272be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F211816_73a6e0cc9d0b3ee65c4cd98d5cc272be.jpg&h=cebc54b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/211837_fe14560585588c8188061192c592df12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F211837_fe14560585588c8188061192c592df12.jpg&h=59e2ed06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個mon真係好正，夠大夠流暢 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/211904_ad58be9d6c41bad348286405c82364f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F211904_ad58be9d6c41bad348286405c82364f6.jpg&h=2677f52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始天黑 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/212106_6c603a4f79b2e01b274b7305ee80bfe2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F212106_6c603a4f79b2e01b274b7305ee80bfe2.jpg&h=85efb7c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/212136_63520b0fbb405d554c163e8eb9fd0c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F212136_63520b0fbb405d554c163e8eb9fd0c16.jpg&h=02ae99e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/212241_5cf4e983bae222b7a4e7a9b02f7f8c4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F212241_5cf4e983bae222b7a4e7a9b02f7f8c4d.jpg&h=63470afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想開套戲睇，迎來一段咁有意思嘅廣告，即刻cap低 <br />\n<br />\nWe travel, not to escape life, but for life not to escape us. <br />\nFor the new perspectives and what remains to be discovered. <br />\nFor the experiences we've acquired and those still yet to come. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/212621_ac37339d85515dcb814790bba3403750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F212621_ac37339d85515dcb814790bba3403750.jpg&h=207ef04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/212643_2aa5dea2d0e2182a8f7647a8c4d6b2b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F212643_2aa5dea2d0e2182a8f7647a8c4d6b2b4.jpg&h=910fa40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/212658_c935268b59f8ab98ba86b41b8f836759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F212658_c935268b59f8ab98ba86b41b8f836759.jpg&h=bc7c1ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/213225_b5f003aa51c6519acf80d37ed924fe0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F213225_b5f003aa51c6519acf80d37ed924fe0d.jpg&h=0ce85193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/213243_6eee1353cefc089c6daa3c9547b704bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F213243_6eee1353cefc089c6daa3c9547b704bd.jpg&h=c96b15d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nReady to take off, Bye Hong Kong <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/213534_5e0b74607416ff0692509b18ad02741f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F213534_5e0b74607416ff0692509b18ad02741f.jpg&h=a38261f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/213621_9128dc3adc728ea20f4dd7b8baac5d89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F213621_9128dc3adc728ea20f4dd7b8baac5d89.jpg&h=6940f76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇期望嘅飛J餐 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/213641_f79849545e7ce2c5a8e71708e4497669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F213641_f79849545e7ce2c5a8e71708e4497669.jpg&h=51e64214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/213655_348a22508a839a174d108c2abfefcdae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F213655_348a22508a839a174d108c2abfefcdae.jpg&h=e2f30c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多得隔離兩位阿嬸，成程機都冇乜點訓，佢地真係可以傾足成程[fuck] ，包括好難得關哂燈嘅時候，點解依家新機設計都係要3個一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/214051_3bcce58c08c5750af0e074ae4f0eb727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F214051_3bcce58c08c5750af0e074ae4f0eb727.jpg&h=dc164341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早餐，西式同粥梗係揀西式，聽到空姐講西式所剩無幾 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/214159_31ab915b5c171868afc1a8207c643d0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F214159_31ab915b5c171868afc1a8207c643d0d.jpg&h=ecef4e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大雨到hi hi <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/214253_c2059ff03995ce18192f7f7a1502ab10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F214253_c2059ff03995ce18192f7f7a1502ab10.jpg&h=53e70906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然好多人都話CX空姐成日黑面，今次負責我呢區嘅空姐又幾好笑容，樣又唔差，有D似 viutv 嘅yoshi, ig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yoshi.1c/?hl=zh-hk \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyoshi.1c%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk%20&d=P1oYep0EJcSam1n0wmqeCsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=b4d77567\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yoshi.1c/?hl=zh-hk </a> <br />\n所以CX之後嘅email 問卷，crew呢part我都比左9分 <br />\n<br />\n經過9個幾鐘機程，終於抵達 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/214326_cb373b98e4a5a849468c991afcf18378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F214326_cb373b98e4a5a849468c991afcf18378.jpg&h=006c6a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用特區護照入境，比人指左去自助入境果邊，我都係想儲個入境印都唔得 <br />\n之後過海關都好順利，冇乜問野冇check行李，正式開始澳洲之旅!"},{"pid":"a1b7d61f90c89cda6b0b1afbf2e23a455cdcbe49","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"過完關之後，就即刻係個gip度拎番件長袖衫著，由一個30度嘅地方去到得番7度嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n跟住買Skybus車票，來回一次過買，約HK$230，車程30min<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/134354_818273d63856b2cdd8cc358af54e2381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F134354_818273d63856b2cdd8cc358af54e2381.jpg&h=b2dc0d59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSkybus 嘅終站係southern cross 南十字星車站，如果你嘅酒店唔係呢度附近，Skybus 係仲有免費接駁服務去附近嘅地方，咁我就唔需要喇，因為酒店就係southern cross站嘅對面<br />\n<br />\nAtlantis Hotel，今次會入住3晚，首先放低行李先，時間只係9am<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/134455_4040d643aaef87470b298e071c7425ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F134455_4040d643aaef87470b298e071c7425ce.jpg&h=858af46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就四周圍散策，率先去地標之一，弗林德斯車站Flinders Street station<br />\n可惜天陰陰，雨勢有時頗大，點影都唔靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/140548_a098e5d38dbd2c5e088495f50f00b03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F140548_a098e5d38dbd2c5e088495f50f00b03b.jpg&h=aba5f04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/140606_89c5ed9ba33a9b4c9cfe4eef19865648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F140606_89c5ed9ba33a9b4c9cfe4eef19865648.jpg&h=20f3ad98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯邦廣場Federation Square<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/140925_1a7d0701e2e504394c675826dbd17e3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F140925_1a7d0701e2e504394c675826dbd17e3c.jpg&h=3442c83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHosier Lane塗鴉巷<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/141102_1afbd64535319b547fadaea1aa9f2fe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F141102_1afbd64535319b547fadaea1aa9f2fe0.jpg&h=e7b9969e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係唔係好識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/141148_03efc1427450b98b451c8621730b3f2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F141148_03efc1427450b98b451c8621730b3f2f.jpg&h=f908b207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRoyal Arcade 皇家拱廊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/141343_63665bcd1eb6110d7533e705e1ded0ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F141343_63665bcd1eb6110d7533e705e1ded0ac.jpg&h=c27d77d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界十大著名圖書館之一 維多利亞州立圖書館 State Library of Victoria<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/141745_fdd7d0b310f0347a1e5a5dd97ad8b299.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F141745_fdd7d0b310f0347a1e5a5dd97ad8b299.jpg&h=a19c5575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再去埋附近嘅維多利亞市場Queen Victoria Market<br />\n呢度真係乜都有，海鮮、肉類、蔬果、熟食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/141938_fedef8f5e502c66561899395e46a0b48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F141938_fedef8f5e502c66561899395e46a0b48.jpg&h=1b88f319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/142154_355879efa39b854f3a2c2ad7f270c8d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F142154_355879efa39b854f3a2c2ad7f270c8d4.jpg&h=62a515c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/142720_60094c34c96c607b576a5e034eb3e490.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F142720_60094c34c96c607b576a5e034eb3e490.jpg&h=1b8f2b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/142752_2d5ed78b9def2a19c8aed86d8d1c4445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F142752_2d5ed78b9def2a19c8aed86d8d1c4445.jpg&h=0877392f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好出名嘅熱狗店，但唔係好識嗌，求其叫左個，盛惠AUD7.2，包皮好硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/142223_280227787b1359f2967149541b2ac2f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F142223_280227787b1359f2967149541b2ac2f7.jpg&h=0cd6e101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/142249_eb78dc842218bcffb89bc844f3ff7219.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F142249_eb78dc842218bcffb89bc844f3ff7219.jpg&h=b6a31e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大雨到hi hi，拿臨衝過橋嘅另一面嘅DFO outlet<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/142903_fd0cbdc9c99dbbe2de8ebcce9a0b1a7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F142903_fd0cbdc9c99dbbe2de8ebcce9a0b1a7c.jpg&h=99d0c452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常大brand都可以係呢度搵到，Adidas  Nike  Vans  New balance，值得一提嘅係Levis 做緊半價，AUD60 (~HK$350) 一條牛，即刻入左兩條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/143732_2ac610dc4f722d4a491c7a5d4d986bea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F143732_2ac610dc4f722d4a491c7a5d4d986bea.jpg&h=18abbce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然已經到左lunch time，DFO入面亦都有food court，不過唔算好肚餓，所以就由佢，差唔多兩點就去酒店check in<br />\n<br />\n約HK$600一晚，房都算幾大，不過打掃得唔乾淨，好明顯牆邊位有塵<br />\n<br />\n澳洲酒店要注意嘅係，多數唔會提供牙刷牙膏，所以我都自備左，係估唔到淋浴露都冇，要用番梘<br />\n<br />\nBook酒店嘅時候本身發現有奇怪位，一d比較平少少嘅酒店係冇free WiFi, 咁佢寫明冇，<br />\n我咪book其他貴少少嘅酒店，去到book呢一間自稱四星級兼有free WiFi 嘅洒店，DKLM，到頭來Free只係限速限量，其他額外收費，OK u win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/144344_39bf2f8756a506ee4ff87b38f03f53ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F144344_39bf2f8756a506ee4ff87b38f03f53ef.jpg&h=3137d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/144409_1e40adf8531785d30ddc27bf9502f572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F144409_1e40adf8531785d30ddc27bf9502f572.jpg&h=bd4b5c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/144446_5672e313c664b14a7b84d9ca7c168a5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F144446_5672e313c664b14a7b84d9ca7c168a5f.jpg&h=22e0627a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係酒店休息到5pm，再次出發行半個鐘左右，到唐人街附近勇記越南河<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/144614_ab49cbac2273a7bb3e6ebe82577d05c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F144614_ab49cbac2273a7bb3e6ebe82577d05c7.jpg&h=8f444b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去過越南之後，都對pho 念念不忘，一直都好想食返果種味道，可惜香港冇一間合格<br />\n至於墨爾本呢間，只可以話係貼近，不過湯底唔夠濃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/144527_c17fae9768eaaad6e6e076f13cb58fee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F144527_c17fae9768eaaad6e6e076f13cb58fee.jpg&h=852833ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/144552_c3a813d0887b631e4f5c7fdc0ba22496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F144552_c3a813d0887b631e4f5c7fdc0ba22496.jpg&h=9951a52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完之後，逛下附近幾條街同shopping mall，7pm就返酒店，因為真係好眼訓<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 完"},{"pid":"f817a018762931cc59a37bc64abad21df192759c","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"Day 3<br />\n<br />\n一起身食返個酒店早餐先，冇為意book酒店果陣有冇包埋早餐，只係見佢房卡套寫breakfast available on G/F，咁咪入去食囉，最後食左三日，都係一模一樣嘅款式<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/152521_f29b4858fc7799624b6aa8791c34e180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F152521_f29b4858fc7799624b6aa8791c34e180.jpg&h=01b4023e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係KXXXL book 左菲利浦島Phillip Island 1 day tour，佢地嘅partner go west 準時11:15am 係酒店門口接上車，司機兼任導遊，其實都唔係介紹左好多野，而架車嘅座位都幾窄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/153023_a53a07a020b42a0e244d7531b45d796e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F153023_a53a07a020b42a0e244d7531b45d796e.jpg&h=832c8de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接齊所有團友都已經12點，有成一半人都係香港人，第一個景點彩虹小屋，好很多人，想影一張冇人嘅相都好難，但係導遊只係安排左逗留20min，好快行個圈影幾張相就要走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/153440_10ff7f64462bf1f0453b938025434be8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F153440_10ff7f64462bf1f0453b938025434be8.jpg&h=b9702531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/153535_986610af7b5bfc6129b3c847b8d2a37c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F153535_986610af7b5bfc6129b3c847b8d2a37c.jpg&h=0fd21cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/153552_959e755a47593394e5b8dd5c49c132ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F153552_959e755a47593394e5b8dd5c49c132ac.jpg&h=f5efd974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/153346_f7f6ca5e03049c272d9259444fd7ca37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F153346_f7f6ca5e03049c272d9259444fd7ca37.jpg&h=6d80435f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二個景點 月光野生動物保育公園Moonlit Sanctuary Wildlife Conservation Park<br />\n<br />\n原本都以為係一個普通動物園，但入到去發現袋鼠區係冇欄杆，佢地見到人就即刻衝過黎，第一下真係比佢地嚇親，大少少嘅袋鼠好似隻恐龍咁衝過黎，之後都試下摸下細隻D嘅袋鼠，都幾乖同可愛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/153927_af426e7ededa7c047f3387665fdb9257.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F153927_af426e7ededa7c047f3387665fdb9257.jpg%20&h=5634a221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/155355_6454afdc246674ce4f4b090822e3b55b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F155355_6454afdc246674ce4f4b090822e3b55b.jpg&h=884ce176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/155541_29a249aa07d008e0e1c4f7a4614bdb04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F155541_29a249aa07d008e0e1c4f7a4614bdb04.jpg&h=b669cd96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/155432_7e7aa2e68e4fa42946735a5fbe8517fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F155432_7e7aa2e68e4fa42946735a5fbe8517fb.jpg&h=341c83af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/155612_7fb4e72325584c65d7ee5a488f8077a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F155612_7fb4e72325584c65d7ee5a488f8077a3.jpg&h=8ce2bb91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/155654_becfa5739a06a772daad0e8b8cfdc4e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F155654_becfa5739a06a772daad0e8b8cfdc4e7.jpg&h=4259ad08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/155823_11d24d8b5a459b860337ff9f298df882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F155823_11d24d8b5a459b860337ff9f298df882.jpg&h=0dc6d949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/155840_2f41515d11908feafc68617245053a0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F155840_2f41515d11908feafc68617245053a0f.jpg&h=af4eefbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨走前睇左一場雀鳥show，都係介紹返一D特別品種嘅雀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/160043_a7ff36f9da06dca5b9b04079ff169925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F160043_a7ff36f9da06dca5b9b04079ff169925.jpg&h=45b3fa0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/160121_e0157399e322390396695dd592b8660b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F160121_e0157399e322390396695dd592b8660b.jpg&h=680213d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3eef395e78e4f406b9ee8ee0e194bc17a5bacef1","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"第三個景點Nobbies諾比斯<br />\n<br />\n正式踏入左菲利普島的西南面，據說呢度係海鳥的棲地，亦可以觀賞海豹<br />\n但係，導遊只係安排左逗留20min，而且個景吸引好多，冇留意有咩動物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/160201_73220eacba9b9e4ae567f9124db6df55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F160201_73220eacba9b9e4ae567f9124db6df55.jpg&h=2425f0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/160219_adcdd857c04a7e344abc7a52ec8c321f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F160219_adcdd857c04a7e344abc7a52ec8c321f.jpg&h=06b09f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/160251_bc5624f6fd51eeeb75230d13b0522efe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F160251_bc5624f6fd51eeeb75230d13b0522efe.jpg&h=8275f40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/160314_fd4cda0b757dafb7690c547184561afc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F160314_fd4cda0b757dafb7690c547184561afc.jpg&h=9f5d5aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一站 今日主角Penguin Parade<br />\n<br />\n呢度就係睇企鵝返屋企，每一朝，企鵝都會成群結隊出海搵野食，直至太陽落山，佢地就會由大海返番沙灘上嘅洞穴<br />\n<br />\n由於相機嘅光會令企鵝短暫失明，所以已經規定左唔比影相<br />\n<br />\n係海邊坐左45min，同時間亦都吹左45min風，終於見到有企鵝上岸，佢地會睇情況，先決定向唔向前行，有時會好似嚇親無端端衝返落海<br />\n<br />\n係看台上面，其實距離都幾遠，但原來由看台行返去出入口嘅路，企鵝仔都會一齊行，呢個時候先可以近距離睇下企鵝仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/160530_0a0cab0f2f975a1d008798bb1fe6be68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F160530_0a0cab0f2f975a1d008798bb1fe6be68.jpg&h=8e82ac1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/001119_b1021ca7218c1112ac6c4a8e513ce988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F001119_b1021ca7218c1112ac6c4a8e513ce988.jpg&h=7fb11731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://penguins.org.au/assets/Uploads/Penguin-Parade-11-small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpenguins.org.au%2Fassets%2FUploads%2FPenguin-Parade-11-small.jpg&h=0934d39d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後搭兩個鐘車出返市區，時間都差唔多9pm，唯有係酒店附近買外賣，照燒雞飯(一D都唔覺有燒過)+天婦羅炸蝦 AUD13.9 (~HKD82)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/160731_9db7f0119093ef775401286a64e40b51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F160731_9db7f0119093ef775401286a64e40b51.jpg&h=335e9b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 3完"},{"pid":"df26468bca9b9f54ed325fdd078aef3d3911d56b","tid":723721,"uid":179414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:03:33.000Z","msg":"留名~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9252f846ff25ce13bcd7db6642c0957821a796be","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"Day 4<br />\n<br />\n今日join左個大洋路1 day tour 中文團，一半人係講廣東話，一半人係講普通話，<br />\n首先集合地點係唐人街，由酒店行過去30min<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/125738_8a495b081aac9d756bdd0e3faa866db5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F125738_8a495b081aac9d756bdd0e3faa866db5.jpg&h=de218fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/125808_86c5a15c5989584aa6b00434283d9f87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F125808_86c5a15c5989584aa6b00434283d9f87.jpg&h=24f125f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車程都差唔多成2個鐘，亦都係司機兼任導遊，導遊會係一D景點放低我地，時間大約都係得20min<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/125846_984e976fc2f68987b52aa5d6cc3cb513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F125846_984e976fc2f68987b52aa5d6cc3cb513.jpg&h=810c2d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/125932_8a3d399243f65c0cdb80bc6779f4fb61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F125932_8a3d399243f65c0cdb80bc6779f4fb61.jpg&h=7c2ab284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/130005_fbcefe666a8bc2d3d4b81b1ea33f3cb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F130005_fbcefe666a8bc2d3d4b81b1ea33f3cb4.jpg&h=d29bf0ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/130038_a8db852d7e2299b9986aefa9ae96168d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F130038_a8db852d7e2299b9986aefa9ae96168d.jpg&h=458224b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導遊係Apollo Bay放低我地，有1hour 食lunch，求其揀左一間中式餐廳食牛河，AUD17.8 (~HKD105)，好撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/130111_aef5151beba4ee059805d33978274ca0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F130111_aef5151beba4ee059805d33978274ca0.jpg&h=d8812d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/130130_f7d015e95b0a830868da2697ecf42500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F130130_f7d015e95b0a830868da2697ecf42500.jpg&h=56d93725&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09a0dadd9e04cbcbd5fe61ebdf0be230c66b90e2","tid":723721,"uid":4160,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:26:14.000Z","msg":"向乜野左右走 高登咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae225a3357db08bb58f76a6effd7194eed3dc3a","tid":723721,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048868742236c0b63df1292f74f058ad5190216d","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"食完飯就繼續出發，開開下車司機突然停車，同我地講有樹熊過馬路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135017_b8b242bb08f2e60d165d3573b36b4d35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135017_b8b242bb08f2e60d165d3573b36b4d35.jpg&h=21a4faa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135057_a021cfb7cc52d7344ee879aa40f9857e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135057_a021cfb7cc52d7344ee879aa40f9857e.jpg&h=2196879a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就到今日重點十二門徒石<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135135_d139bb73626fae8e9ba6d4bcf949cf67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135135_d139bb73626fae8e9ba6d4bcf949cf67.jpg&h=21c78961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135205_20925b82223bf32f25b78ce265c11c1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135205_20925b82223bf32f25b78ce265c11c1a.jpg&h=112bc2f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一個景點，洛克峽谷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135319_348dc06dd213375576dec3d05b537dbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135319_348dc06dd213375576dec3d05b537dbd.jpg&h=7061a161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135339_1bf2e43d6567b57f2e1492d8b42075df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135339_1bf2e43d6567b57f2e1492d8b42075df.jpg&h=e02d4f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實跟中文團，本身都預左多大陸人，雖然今次只得一半，不過佢地真係唔係好理導遊講嘅集合時間，有時仲要遲十五分鍾，都幾無奈<br />\n<br />\n返番市區之後，就到Melbourne Central Shopping Centre 食呢間被譽為澳洲最好食漢堡包<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135428_123e56c259d12ee58916e9204382a6bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135428_123e56c259d12ee58916e9204382a6bb.jpg&h=d53ffb26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以比你自己揀想要咩包皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135457_611f18dff6f3e5c930135579ad820236.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135457_611f18dff6f3e5c930135579ad820236.jpg&h=618d3eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係好睇得明個menu，求其叫左個+薯條 AUD18 (~HKD106)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135520_38d6817ed90aae4df0f0edb51210e580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135520_38d6817ed90aae4df0f0edb51210e580.jpg&h=54ec2617&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e53b019d0b8a602581ff90911891344d604c48e","tid":723721,"uid":52833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:03:20.000Z","msg":"Lm 加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa8c0f602f519d37830c7f44f33b0da3b20b1d4","tid":723721,"uid":19485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8月去Melbourne 10日<br />\n幾年前探親去過一次,無去過乜野地方,<br />\n今次諗緊去唔去Philip island<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n想去puffing billy 同 Sovereign Hill<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f425117a38654d98873bdc312b5d0795fc895f43","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caa8c0f602f519d37830c7f44f33b0da3b20b1d4","tid":723721,"uid":19485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8月去Melbourne 10日<br />\n幾年前探親去過一次,無去過乜野地方,<br />\n今次諗緊去唔去Philip island<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n想去puffing billy 同 Sovereign Hill<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T07:58:12.000Z","msg":"Melbourne 景點選擇唔多，去10日應該都係去呢d地方<br />\nPhilip island值得一去嘅，可惜唔可以影下企鵝<br />\npuffing billy 我出發前睇到notice話之前有意外，所以唔可以伸手腳出車外，我覺得吸引力大減，所以放棄左<br />\nSovereign hill 我就覺得悶悶地而且入場費貴，所以冇去"},{"pid":"d4972e20980c7e44db238082dae7b42220484727","tid":723721,"uid":109047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:01:58.000Z","msg":"LM!下個月去"},{"pid":"e8f84cab3cb624b53eb78292eb4a6220fa2c5a9b","tid":723721,"uid":11672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"究竟乜野人先會人手filter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b916804ca152b82fc84867160fe1038e07094035","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"Day 5<br />\n今日會離開墨爾本，搭澳洲航空內陸機去悉尼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/134637_91a0353304210e2924fb4dbe030c7c5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F134637_91a0353304210e2924fb4dbe030c7c5d.jpg&h=e62e8f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n專登揀班A330，以為大機有電視，結果都係冇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/134658_2eae23fdbbc24fd747978db96a1b08bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F134658_2eae23fdbbc24fd747978db96a1b08bc.jpg&h=fadf9c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備降落時已經見到港灣大橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/134745_d2673f126195171512c4ba0d2c8b1689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F134745_d2673f126195171512c4ba0d2c8b1689.jpg&h=12950f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭機場快線，一個大城市通勤線用雙層真係好少見<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/134839_f06ac0d5045cddb4789fb0508360f322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F134839_f06ac0d5045cddb4789fb0508360f322.jpg&h=bfe486c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後黎左呢架咁殘舊嘅火車<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/134910_1fc8bba92bf76931d8508edc553ee633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F134910_1fc8bba92bf76931d8508edc553ee633.jpg&h=8eab7e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去酒店放低行李之後就立即出發去fish market<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/134942_5c4e1f6196cc4b1d886cc01c1b95e6d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F134942_5c4e1f6196cc4b1d886cc01c1b95e6d3.jpg&h=429a5761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135012_6deb1ef3b773fa5af3e3002215d8f0fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135012_6deb1ef3b773fa5af3e3002215d8f0fb.jpg&h=ee93e510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135036_4330f89bde8c4088d4117f16310677f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135036_4330f89bde8c4088d4117f16310677f2.jpg&h=86359621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到芝士焗扇貝新鮮出爐，即刻叫返個，AUD3.5 (~HKD20)，味道不過不失啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135101_0d1fe0b30a319e56dce058a2b30f37d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135101_0d1fe0b30a319e56dce058a2b30f37d7.jpg&h=582d0519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就叫左個三文魚壽司，AUD10 (~HKD60)，非常之垃圾，同日本比差好遠，魚冇鮮味，飯係完全冇黏性嘅硬飯粒，一夾即散<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135132_4d501e2c5fb85b17ef41a69d414aed33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135132_4d501e2c5fb85b17ef41a69d414aed33.jpg&h=ea42c2b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a497185b1634b17e56be60952948c094b975664f","tid":723721,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"見其他野都冇乜好食同抵食，就出發去港灣大橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135225_74d5624ee9d81a1d172c8efc06c6a4ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135225_74d5624ee9d81a1d172c8efc06c6a4ca.jpg&h=a8ec973f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再到隔離嘅歌劇院<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135319_3d57e44b74c61a2cfe830e2dde525127.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135319_3d57e44b74c61a2cfe830e2dde525127.jpg&h=3c99ba4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就去唐人街附近嘅Paddy&rsquo;s market，類似女人街嘅地方，係呢度買手信真係好抵，同一樣嘅產品起碼平一半<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135420_aac707049cc23de533cdf74d6beefaee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135420_aac707049cc23de533cdf74d6beefaee.jpg&h=2cb7d28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135508_51a6c84f7ca4384cf86cf98ff480a118.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135508_51a6c84f7ca4384cf86cf98ff480a118.jpg&h=08977bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再出去睇下darling harbour嘅夜景<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135541_6e29287b391ccbadc1bc474053632834.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135541_6e29287b391ccbadc1bc474053632834.jpg&h=d267b2a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肚餓就去返Paddy&rsquo;s market上面market city嘅food court<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135602_81ba2294261ffbae1f4ef16a38e4e4e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135602_81ba2294261ffbae1f4ef16a38e4e4e0.jpg&h=228fac10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135630_d6fc776513e38982dae6e4112a4f7985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135630_d6fc776513e38982dae6e4112a4f7985.jpg&h=15c58cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾貼近香港口味嘅楊州炒飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/135648_d0ec17be660c8b68ba475531ba286983.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F135648_d0ec17be660c8b68ba475531ba286983.jpg&h=bc93c860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 5完"},{"pid":"3ce09dfa282ed03e658a42850e4da4924c2fd2c3","tid":723721,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"